## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all possible actions for environmental protection. The information is subject to change as new research and policies emerge. Additionally, the effectiveness of the suggested actions can vary based on geographic and socio-economic contexts. Further research and localized studies are recommended for a more comprehensive understanding.